# 🏥 Online Medical Store

A modern full-stack Online Medical Store web application that allows users to browse medicines, search products, add items to the cart, place orders, and manage their accounts. The application is built using React for the frontend, Node.js & Express.js for the backend, and MongoDB as the database.

---

## 🚀 Features

### 👤 User Features
- User Registration & Login
- Secure Authentication
- Browse Medicines
- Search Medicines
- Filter by Category
- Product Details Page
- Shopping Cart
- Checkout System
- Order History
- User Profile Management

### 🛠️ Admin Features
- Admin Dashboard
- Add Medicines
- Update Medicines
- Delete Medicines
- Manage Categories
- Manage Orders
- Manage Users
- Inventory Management

