## ⚙️ Installation

### Clone Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/online-medical-store.git
```

```bash
cd online-medical-store
```

---

## Install Frontend

```bash
cd client
npm install
```

Start Frontend

```bash
npm start
```

---

## Install Backend

```bash
cd server
npm install
```

Start Backend

```bash
npm run dev
```

---

## Environment Variables

Create a `.env` file inside the **server** folder.

```env
PORT=5000

MONGO_URI=your_mongodb_connection_string

JWT_SECRET=your_secret_key

NODE_ENV=development
```

---

## API Endpoints

### Authentication

```
POST   /api/auth/register
POST   /api/auth/login
GET    /api/auth/profile
```

### Medicines

```
GET     /api/medicines
GET     /api/medicines/:id
POST    /api/medicines
PUT     /api/medicines/:id
DELETE  /api/medicines/:id
```

### Orders

```
POST   /api/orders
GET    /api/orders
GET    /api/orders/:id
```

### Users

```
GET    /api/users
PUT    /api/users/:id
DELETE /api/users/:id
```

